layers to approach every angle of the environment.\nDiverse worlds: Each world in the application has its own theme and challenges, ranging from simple to complex environments.\nEnvironmental interaction: Cube blocks can interact with elements in the environment, creating interesting effects and outcomes.\nIn-app purchases (IAP): Players can unlock additional new worlds through the in-app purchase system, expanding their gaming experience and exploration.\nVivid graphics: Sharp 3D images and bright colors create an engaging and vibrant VR world.", "short_description": "Interaction World Cube is an innovative and interactive virtual reality (VR) application designed to provide a unique experience for VR headset users. In this virtual world, players explore and interact with the environment by controlling various cube blocks."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://doc-hosting.flycricket.io/interaction-world-cube-privacy-policy/08221178-c069-446b-92e7-5084b550f81f/privacy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://doc-hosting.flycricket.io/interaction-world-cube-terms-of-use/559a5238-2fc1-4366-b76f-caf297bbad12/terms", "publisher_name": "Brittany Monique Patton", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://46935909.hubspotpagebuilder.com/en-us/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1990104051447093"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "7521661961272633"}}]}, "scheduled_off